      "patch": "@@ -3,9 +3,16 @@\n Code and data for \"MemOps: Benchmarking Lifecycle Memory\n Operations in Long-Horizon Conversations\".\n \n+MemOps builds long, noisy multi-session conversations that plant verifiable\n+personal facts (\"evidence\") among distractors and irrelevant chit-chat, then\n+benchmarks how well different memory strategies can recall and\n+update those facts over the conversation's lifecycle.\n \n ## Pipeline\n \n+![MemOps Pipeline](img/generation_pipeline.png)\n+\n+\n | Step | Script | Purpose |\n |---|---|---|\n | 1 | `1-generate_background.py` | Generate personal background descriptions from `info/topics.md` |"
